    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005350/extras/9d0a46d0345c9acf0e7542665b13e260.avif?t=1770678438\" width=600 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seven people awaken in the Moirae facility with months of their memories erased. A mysterious figure informs them that the path to freedom will open only when they confess to their forgotten sins. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reflection Link is a mystery game featuring escape-room style puzzles, branching paths, and a cast with queer relationships and hidden connections that shape how the story unfolds. Your choices impact how the group interprets events, how their relationships evolve, and which truths come to light.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005350/extras/e8ef95c982178b57c935af9d6b0636fa.poster.avif?t=1770678438\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005350/extras/e8ef95c982178b57c935af9d6b0636fa.webm?t=1770678438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005350/extras/e8ef95c982178b57c935af9d6b0636fa.mp4?t=1770678438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the facility:</strong> Use point-and-click gameplay to search, disassemble and combine items, decipher clues, enter passwords, and uncover memory fragments on each floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005350/extras/4087a9aecb2b5c7f7c542bc8a5d564d2.poster.avif?t=1770678438\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005350/extras/4087a9aecb2b5c7f7c542bc8a5d564d2.webm?t=1770678438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005350/extras/4087a9aecb2b5c7f7c542bc8a5d564d2.mp4?t=1770678438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Lead Discussions:</strong> Guide tense group conversations by selecting and combining talking points. Uncover the truth behind the captives' circumstances and their connections to each other. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005350/extras/56d70fb41af2ea030ef8dd88e5d1cc64.poster.avif?t=1770678438\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005350/extras/56d70fb41af2ea030ef8dd88e5d1cc64.webm?t=1770678438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005350/extras/56d70fb41af2ea030ef8dd88e5d1cc64.mp4?t=1770678438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relive memories:</strong> Use the timeline system to revisit previous routes and open new branches. Discover the key to freedom.</p>",
